description: A young car and bike racer came to my office looking for work. The guy was good, he even won a few trophies. His parents stopped supporting him, so he had to find a proper job and take care of himself. He was nice and polite but not very talkative. His melancholic mood was most probably caused by a recent break-up. The young man was a trained and experienced car mechanic, so I gave him a very nice job at a repair shop. I hoped it would help him. But first he had to do me a little favor. Our fee was way too much for him, so my help was required. I was very horny today, so the guy had to challenge his sexuality a little. Probably way more than he ever expected. Convincing him wasn't a problem, he was greedy as hell. Maybe he thought it was going to be easy...
title: Dirty Scout 209
